                                    >年間<span class="txt__strong">48</span
                                    >万円！</span
                                >
                                <span class="Local"
                                    ><span class="txt__bg"
                                        >月<span class="txt__strong">4</span
                                        >万円の利益</span
                                    >が出せる計算！</span
                                >
