                                    <source
                                        media="(max-width:767px)"
                                        srcset="/asset/images/recipe/2x/img_recipe_result_Cost_02@2x.png"
                                    />
                                    <img
                                        src="/asset/images/recipe/img_recipe_result_Cost_02.png"
                                        srcset="/asset/images/recipe/img_recipe_result_Cost_02.png 1x,/asset/images/recipe/2x/img_recipe_result_Cost_02@2x.png 2x"
                                        alt=""
                                        width="299"
                                        height="131"
                                        loading="lazy"
                                        class="imgauto"
                                    />
                                </picture>
                            </span>
                        </p>
                        <p class="Cost__bottomRight">
                            <span class="txt__bg"
                                >失われている利益を取り戻せる!</span
